title: Clara Honsinger, Eric Brunner Ride into Stars and Stripes at US Cyclocross Nationals
content:
Honsinger, Brunner continue to dominate with fourth and second elite titles respectively after gritty racing in Louisville.

Read the full article at Clara Honsinger, Eric Brunner Ride into Stars and Stripes at US Cyclocross Nationals on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
